{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Imports annotation TXT files and creates REAPER regions starting at the current edit cursor position. Commonly used for Chirpity, Audacity, BirdNET, or similar annotation exports.\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 \fmodern Courier;}}
