{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Pre-populates Project Render Metadata with all UCS / Extended / ASWG keys (same mapping as acendan_UCS Renaming Tool) without renaming anything. Run before opening the Render dialog so fields aren\u8217't empty.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 By default writes $marker(Field)[;] substitutions (dynamic). Optional: set direct_values = true to write current extstate literal values instead.\par}
}

